embeds.title: Saragon
embeds.description:
Hi I'm Raven,

I first used chromeOS in school and liked how cost effective the OS was so my first personal computer was a chromebook around 2015 years ago.

I've been on discord since 2016 and have built and moderated several personal servers and communities.

Currently I am learning Java against my will, but still prefer using python and admire golang from afar.
